Returning to the UK
When you return, you must follow the rules for entering the UK.
Further information
Guatemalan authorities request that people keep up to date with the latest restrictions by visiting the following official page where all important information about COVID-19 as well as all advice from the Guatemalan Ministry of Health can be found.
If you need urgent consular assistance, contact your nearest British embassy, high commission or consulate. All telephone numbers are available 24/7.
